metadata.name: Mutant Ape Kid #1
metadata.description: Public Mint is currently Live: https://www.mutantapekidsclub.com. Become an Mutant Ape Kid. As an MAKC member, you can own any of the 6,969 Kid Apes, thoughtfully recreated into unique AI-generated Kid Ape Paintings. Only one painting will be minted for each Kid Ape, and 24 distinct AI-models have been applied across the collection, to help create value for the owner of every individual ERC-721 token. Each mint of Kid Ape Art will be eligible for future drops of specially designed frames to highlight your fine art.
